      <title>特朗普希望在豁免裁决后暂停秘密记录案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-wants-florida-documents-case-paused-after-supreme-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院裁定前总统唐纳德·特朗普可能免于与官方行为相关的刑事指控，之后他要求暂停因涉嫌不当处理机密信息而进行的起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-wants-florida-documents-case-paused-after-supreme-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 18:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒙蒂称法国尚未成熟，无法接受意大利式的技术官僚统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/france-isn-t-ripe-for-italy-style-technocrat-reign-monti-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利前总理马里奥·蒙蒂表示，由技术官僚领导的法国联合政府不太可能立即解决周日立法选举中可能出现的政治僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/france-isn-t-ripe-for-italy-style-technocrat-reign-monti-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 18:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调解员将在最新一轮谈判后继续加沙停火谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/mediators-set-to-continue-gaza-truce-talks-after-latest-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[调解人员将继续在以色列和哈马斯之间进行间接谈判，以期弥合拟议停火协议中剩余的分歧，这是数周来最明显的迹象，表明经过数月的谈判仍未能停止加沙冲突，停火是有可能的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/mediators-set-to-continue-gaza-truce-talks-after-latest-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 18:12:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与盟友推动的第二任期议程划清界限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-denounces-heritage-foundation-s-project-2025-agenda-pushed-by-allies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普谴责了他的一些最亲密的白宫顾问制定的一项全面政策议程，该议程提议对联邦政府进行大规模改革，并在各机构中安插前总统的忠实拥护者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-denounces-heritage-foundation-s-project-2025-agenda-pushed-by-allies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 17:56:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>该团队将执掌英国 14 年来首个工党政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/the-team-set-to-run-the-uk-s-first-labour-government-in-14-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国 14 年来首次工党政府中，担任重要职务的人员包括前英格兰银行经济学家、第一位就读哈佛法学院的英国黑人和前工会工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/the-team-set-to-run-the-uk-s-first-labour-government-in-14-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 16:44:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>身价 140 亿美元的沃尔玛继承人与诺沃格拉茨联手敦促拜登下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/a-14-billion-walmart-heir-joins-novogratz-urging-biden-to-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个由顶级商业领袖组成的联盟正在进一步推动总统乔·拜登放弃竞选连任，并给拜登写了一封由亿万富翁和企业高管签名的信。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/a-14-billion-walmart-heir-joins-novogratz-urging-biden-to-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 14:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国新议会除高层外最为多元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-s-new-parliament-most-diverse-ever-but-not-at-the-top</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国选民周四选出了历史上最多的少数族裔下议院议员，这反映出越来越多的少数族裔参与政治以及政党寻求反映其所代表的民众心声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-s-new-parliament-most-diverse-ever-but-not-at-the-top</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 12:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守党混乱统治后，斯塔默誓言“稳定与温和”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-vows-stability-and-moderation-in-reset-for-uk-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新任首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 率领工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，结束了保守党 14 年动荡内讧的统治，承诺组建一个“稳定与温和”的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-vows-stability-and-moderation-in-reset-for-uk-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 12:14:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙问题使工党英国大选胜利黯然失色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gaza-concerns-take-gloss-off-labour-s-uk-election-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党在英国大选中取得压倒性胜利，但一些令人震惊的失利也令其蒙受损失，因为该党的选票大量流失到在加沙地区竞选的独立人士和城市地区的绿党手中。损失包括党魁凯尔·斯塔默的高层团队的两名成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gaza-concerns-take-gloss-off-labour-s-uk-election-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:06:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列情报局长前往卡塔尔与哈马斯就加沙停火进行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/chief-of-israel-s-mossad-goes-to-qatar-for-talks-with-hamas-on-ceasefire-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解会谈情况的人士透露，由摩萨德负责人戴维·巴尼亚率领的以色列代表团在与哈马斯进行一天的停火协议谈判后，正在从卡塔尔回国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/chief-of-israel-s-mossad-goes-to-qatar-for-talks-with-hamas-on-ceasefire-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:39:32 GMT</pubDate>
